<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class='mx-auto col-11 col-sm-10 col-lg-8 col-xl-6'>
      <h1>welcome to <i class="fas fa-beer"></i><strong>Bounenkai</strong>  !!</h1>
      <p>In  <i class="fas fa-beer"></i><strong>Bounenkai</strong>, </p>
      <p>you can share and exchange  your SAKE , inpressions , and emotions</p>
      <p> about various alcohol!</p>
      <% unless user_signed_in? %>
      <div class="btn-wrapper col-10 mx-auto">
        <div class="row">
          <%= link_to 'Log in',new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-info btn-sm btn-block mb-3 sign_in" %>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <%= link_to 'Sign Up',new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-sm btn-block mb-3 sign_up" %>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <%= link_to 'Danger',danger_path, class: "btn btn-danger btn-sm btn-block sign_up" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% else %>
      <h1>なぜわざわざBounenkaiのタイトルをクリックした？</h1>
      <h1>貴様飲み足りていないな。</h1>
      <h1>4点とビールくれてやろう。（お酒を注文してください）</h1>
      <% end%>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
